1
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:20,440
Why?

2
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,460
Are you still mad at me?

3
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:24,290
I wouldn't dare.

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,480
I was too impulsive before.

5
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:29,000
I shouldn't have locked you up.

6
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,920
I'm sorry. It won't happen again.

7
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:36,180
What are you doing?

8
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:40,450
I was bored, so I'm doing a little experiment.

9
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:44,680
Soap.

10
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,160
My father opened a soap factory recently.

11
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:49,080
So I got interested in this stuff.

12
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,760
I looked into it and found it quite interesting.

13
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:53,290
I can even mix my own scents.

14
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:57,940
Does it smell good?

15
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,580
It's very special.

16
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:07,720
Young Master,

17
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:13,760
Mr. Johnson's subordinate reported

18
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,360
that he wants to visit the Yao Soap Factory the day after tomorrow

19
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:17,160
and hopes you can accompany him.

20
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,340
Okay. Understood.

21
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:25,680
Huainan, I want to go with you the day after tomorrow.

22
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,360
I want to see that professional soap factory

23
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:29,620
and how it differs from my handmade soap.

24
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:30,800
Can I?

25
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:32,360
Sure.

26
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:34,479
I'll take you along the day after tomorrow.

27
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:36,400
I have other business to attend to.

28
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:39,060
Your injury hasn't healed yet. You need to rest.

29
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,120
I'm off.

30
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:58,610
Marshal,

31
00:01:58,960 --> 00:01:59,880
everything you ordered

32
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,760
has been taken care of.

33
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,290
However,

34
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:03,560
Zhu Luoli's body hasn't been found yet.

35
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,000
Since you have the secret recipe,

36
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,860
why haven't I seen you make a move?

37
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,680
Song Huainan is taking foreigners to the factory the day after tomorrow.

38
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,340
I'll find a way to stay behind.

39
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,200
I have a new plan.

40
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,760
My mother gave me a lot of money.

41
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,320
Since you have the secret recipe,

42
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,840
why don't we use this money

43
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,240
to build our own factory?

44
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,800
Okay.

45
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,460
I'll go get things ready for the Yao Factory.

46
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,000
Okay.

47
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,440
Mr. Ambassador,

48
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,360
we're using state-of-the-art equipment.

49
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:27,320
We're mixing strictly according to the secret recipe.

50
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:30,579
The first batch of samples goes into production tomorrow.

51
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:32,600
Boss Yao,

52
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:33,840
you two

53
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,900
must turn them into gold as soon as possible.

54
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,840
Don't worry, Mr. Ambassador.

55
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,410
Mr. Ambassador,

56
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,800
Why don't we return to the Military Department

57
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,880
and discuss another matter?

58
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:46,480
All right.

59
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,650
Father-in-law,

60
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,320
let Shengsheng stay here for a while.

61
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,280
I'll pick her up tonight.

62
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:50,720
Okay.

63
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,560
Please.

64
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,560
I want to stay in the lab

65
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,290
and see if I can improve my soap.

66
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:06,480
What's so fun about this lab?

67
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:09,120
Besides, the sample production tomorrow is very important.

68
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,320
Nothing can go wrong.

69
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,360
Dad, I promise.

70
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,960
I won't disturb their work,

71
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,490
and I won't touch anything.

72
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,360
Besides,

73
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:20,120
you're so busy, you don't have time for me.

74
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,680
I'll be so bored alone at your place,

75
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,600
won't I?

76
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,080
My daughter...

77
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:27,960
Please, Dad.

78
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,320
Okay, okay.

79
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:31,880
Go ahead.

80
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,380
Song Qingzhou.

81
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,490
What a coincidence.

82
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,360
Is something the matter, Master Yao?

83
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:42,220
I actually have a favor to ask of you, Young Marshal.

84
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,490
Go ahead.

85
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,840
Shengsheng is in the factory lab today.

86
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:47,159
My father insisted I buy some pear blossom cakes

87
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,200
and deliver them to her.

88
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,360
But there's a play today,

89
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,159
and I went to great lengths to get tickets.

90
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,520
It's already starting.

91
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:55,890
Could you please deliver them for me, Young Marshal?

92
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,240
Okay.

93
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,940
Thank you, Young Marshal. I'll be going now.

94
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,420
Miss Yao, we're getting off work now.

95
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,280
I'll stay here a little longer.

96
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,940
All right. I'll take my leave.

97
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:45,930
Who's there?

98
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,120
It's me.

99
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,840
Qingzhou, what brings you here?

100
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,280
Your brother asked me to bring you some food.

101
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,080
Thanks to him,

102
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,280
I had the honor of visiting

103
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:01,940
the famous Yao Soap Business.

104
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,000
You know, Yao Lifu

105
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,000
is really good to his sister.

106
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:13,380
It's a shame he's not like that to others.

107
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,520
The other day,

108
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:16,480
he told me

109
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,810
to take good care of you.

110
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,360
Really?

111
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,930
What else did he say?

112
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,200
He also said

113
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,380
he originally wanted you to marry me.

114
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,810
Huainan, what brings you here?

115
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,880
My dad has some premium Longjing tea in his office.

116
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,320
Let's go have a cup together.

117
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:22,920
I'll pass.

118
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,900
I just came to pick up Shengsheng.

119
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,920
Huainan, let's go have a drink.

120
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,840
Song Huainan.

121
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,040
Why are you here all alone?

122
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,100
The workers have all left.

123
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,560
Is this stuff that fun?

124
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,080
To think you're so obsessed.

125
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,280
Huainan, since you're here,

126
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,120
let's go home.

127
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,680
I'm starving from the wait.

128
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,200
Okay, let's go.

129
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,770
Brother, we're going home now.

130
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,010
No need to see us off.

131
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:23,160
Stop hiding. Come out.

132
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,340
Why are you hiding?

133
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,360
I thought you weren't afraid of Song Huainan.

134
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,679
What's it to you?

135
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,240
It's not my business.

136
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,840
I just feel like we're in the same boat.

137
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,160
You clearly like Shengsheng,

138
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,320
but you can only watch her

139
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,160
stay by your brother's side.

140
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,210
Aren't you the same?

141
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,880
Yeah.

142
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,280
In this world,

143
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,920
maybe it's all about the regret of unrequited love.

144
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:58,780
That depends on

145
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,740
whether that person is worth loving.

146
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:56,680
Let's go.
